rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, Rex! Looks like you've got quite
the salvaging business going on there!

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You should bring your haul along
there. Collectibles, treasure,
whatever's in your pockets.

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0003
rows.name:
You'll get a better deal if you can
sell 'em off in bulk.

rows.label: tlk41300011_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Playing the market in your favor
is the mark of a true salvager!
